{"tid":1610193,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"聯署！簽哂佢！","createTime":"2019-10-01T16:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T08:54:59.000Z","uid":279006,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d795e89adff85432fac43c2aa87e8d3b63d88af6","tid":1610193,"uid":279006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:37:42.000Z","msg":"《美國白宮聯署》<br />\n<br />\n1. 請求美國行使《全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法》，制裁侵犯人權的香港官員或知名人士。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2mIGUn2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2mIGUn2&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=3f3d142a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2mIGUn2</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 請求美國拯救香港市民，提供人道救援<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2kk2ZHW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kk2ZHW&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=eae99a0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2kk2ZHW</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 請求美國通過《香港保護法案》，暫停向香港警察出售催淚彈、胡椒噴霧、橡膠子彈和其他防暴物品。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2m39jUJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2m39jUJ&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=f4285c1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2m39jUJ</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 請求美國將香港警察加入《香港人權及民主法案》的制裁名單。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2kyBsT1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kyBsT1&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=9f62a4fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2kyBsT1</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 請求美國承認香港為美國保護區。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2kK8y2q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kK8y2q&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=288603f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2kK8y2q</a>"},{"pid":"d77908799878777a891c39a1f5cccb991d187598","tid":1610193,"uid":249324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:19:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":